<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fernanda Carlim</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --bg2: #111111;
    --bg3: #181818;
    --fg: #f0ede6;
    --fg-muted: rgba(240,237,230,0.45);
    --fg-dim: rgba(240,237,230,0.2);
    --accent: #f0ede6;
    --accent2: rgba(240,237,230,0.6);
    --accent3: rgba(240,237,230,0.8);
    --mono: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    --serif: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--fg);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* CURSOR */
  .cursor {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, background 0.2s;
    mix-blend-mode: difference;
  }
  .cursor.hover { transform: scale(4); background: var(--accent); }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -3px; left: 0;
    width: 0; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--fg); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }
  .nav-links a.active { color: var(--accent); }

  /* LANG SWITCHER */
  .lang-switcher {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin-left: 2rem;
  }
  .lang-btn {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .lang-btn.active {
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .lang-btn:hover:not(.active) {
    border-color: var(--fg);
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  /* PAGES */
  .page { display: none; min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 5rem; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     HOME
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  #home {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  #home.active { display: flex; }

  .home-noise {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .home-grid-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--fg-dim) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--fg-dim) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    opacity: 0.15;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .home-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .home-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s forwards;
  }
  .home-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 40px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .home-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 0.2em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .home-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .home-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .home-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards;
  }

  .tag {
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .home-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1s forwards;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #ffffff; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--fg);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--fg); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .home-number {
    position: fixed;
    right: 2.5rem;
    bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .home-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    z-index: 2;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.2s forwards;
  }
  .home-scroll::after {
    content: '';
    width: 30px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--fg-dim);
    animation: scrollLine 2s 1.5s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollLine {
    0% { width: 30px; opacity: 1; }
    50% { width: 60px; opacity: 0.5; }
    100% { width: 30px; opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     ABOUT
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  #about { padding-top: 8rem; }

  .about-grid {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-left {}

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-bio {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-bio em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }

  .about-body {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-right { padding-top: 4rem; }

  .skills-block {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .skills-block:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .skills-title {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .skills-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-chip {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .skill-chip:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }

  .experience-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .experience-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .exp-company { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .exp-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .exp-year { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--fg-dim); text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     PROJECTS (shared)
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  .projects-page { padding-top: 8rem; }

  .projects-header {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .page-title em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }

  .projects-grid {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    transition: background 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .project-card:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-dim); }

  .project-card:hover { padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; margin: 0 -1rem; }

  .project-num {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    padding-top: 0.4rem;
  }

  .project-body {}

  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .project-card:hover .project-title { color: var(--accent); }

  .project-client {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-desc {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .project-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .project-tag {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
  }

  .project-tag.blue {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    border-color: var(--fg-dim);
  }

  .project-tag.red {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    border-color: var(--fg-dim);
  }

  .project-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    padding-top: 0.2rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .project-card:hover .project-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* Category accent bars */
  .cat-product .project-num::before { content: '◆ '; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .cat-music .project-num::before { content: '◆ '; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .cat-production .project-num::before { content: '◆ '; color: var(--fg-muted); }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     CONTACT
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  #contact { padding-top: 8rem; }

  .contact-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-big {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .contact-big em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }
  .contact-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .contact-item-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .contact-item-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .contact-item-arrow {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     FOOTER
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════
     TICKER
  ═══════════════════════════════ */
  .ticker-wrap {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0.9rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .ticker {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    animation: ticker 30s linear infinite;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ticker span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ticker span.accent { color: var(--fg-muted); }

  @keyframes ticker {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* HIGHLIGHT STRIPE */
  .stripe {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    color: var(--fg);
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    margin: 4rem 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stripe-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    color: var(--fg);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; }
    .home-inner { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .projects-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 0 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .project-card { grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr; }
    .project-arrow { display: none; }
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .projects-grid { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    .contact-inner { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#" onclick="showPage('home')">FC</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('home')" id="nav-home" class="active">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('about')" id="nav-about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('product')" id="nav-product">Product</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('music')" id="nav-music">Music & Culture</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('production')" id="nav-production">Production</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" onclick="showPage('contact')" id="nav-contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="lang-switcher">
    <a class="lang-btn" href="index.html">PT</a>
    <span class="lang-btn active">EN</span>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ════════════ HOME ════════════ -->
<section id="home" class="page active">
  <div class="home-noise"></div>
  <div class="home-grid-lines"></div>
  <div class="home-inner">
    <div class="home-eyebrow">Portfolio — São Paulo, BR</div>
    <h1 class="home-title">Fernanda<br><em>Carlim</em></h1>
    <p class="home-subtitle">
      Digital product and brand management at the intersection of<br>
      technology, culture and creative operations —<br>
      translating complexity into clear, scalable solutions.
    </p>
    <div class="home-tags">
      <span class="tag">Product Management</span>
      <span class="tag">Fintech</span>
      <span class="tag">Creative Operations</span>
      <span class="tag">Music Label</span>
      <span class="tag">São Paulo, BR</span>
    </div>
    <div class="home-cta">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="showPage('product')">View Projects</button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="showPage('about')">About me</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-scroll">scroll</div>
  <div class="home-number">Fernanda Carlim — 2025</div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════ ABOUT ════════════ -->
<section id="about" class="page">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-left">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h2 class="about-bio">
        Where digital product meets <em>creative culture.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="about-body">
        I'm Fe — a digital product and brand management professional working at the intersection of technology, culture and creative operations. I work on the development and evolution of complex digital products, focusing on workflow structuring, continuous improvement, operational efficiency and real business impact.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        I have a background in Communications, a specialization in Cultural Management, and since 2021 I've been deeply involved in digital product work — connecting strategic vision, hands-on execution and a thorough understanding of creative contexts. My experience spans financial products, ERPs, operational platforms and cultural projects, always seeking to translate complexity into clear, scalable and well-structured solutions.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        In parallel, I co-founded the label Perfecto Estado and the platform Cereal Melodia, where I work as executive producer and curator. In personal projects, I explore electronic music and other creative fronts as an extension of my product and culture perspective.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        This duality isn't a conflict — it's what makes me different.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-right">
      <div class="skills-block">
        <div class="skills-title">Product & Tech</div>
        <div class="skills-list">
          <span class="skill-chip">Product Management</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Roadmapping</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">User Research</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Onboarding</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Financial Services</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Payment Gateway</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">SQL</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Analytics</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">CRM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skills-block">
        <div class="skills-title">Culture & Production</div>
        <div class="skills-list">
          <span class="skill-chip">Music Curation</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Executive Production</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Event Management</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Influencer Marketing</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Audiovisual Production</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Art Direction</span>
          <span class="skill-chip">Set Design</span>
